        {
            "+content": "Hiraku, a once sickly and lonely young man, is reincarnated into another world through the grace of the gods. His small farm, created deep in the forest, grows into a lively settlement known as Great Tree Village, attracting a diverse cast of residents, including vampires, elves, beastmen, and angels. His peaceful days are filled with cultivating fields, raising livestock, and sharing laughter with friends. But visitors keep coming, and the village is busier than ever.",
            "+@gid": "1888850757",
            "+@type": "Plot Summary"
